wdi2-SM.POP.TOTL.ZS.def: International migrant stock is the number of people born in a country other than that in which they live, including refugees.
wdi2-SM.POP.TOTL.ZS.name: International migrant stock
wdi2-SM.POP.TOTL.ZS.source: United Nations Population Division, Trends in Total Migrant Stock: 2008 Revision.
